---

# 2.6 Onboarding Task Checklist

### Location

Employee onboarding profile.

### Tasks

* Complete personal details
* Upload required documents
* Accept company policies
* Complete mandatory training

### Functionalities

* Track completion status
* Update progress percentage
* Prevent onboarding completion until all tasks are finished

---

# 2.7 HR Approval Workflow

### Location

Employee onboarding controls.

### Status Types

* Pending
* Approved
* Rejected
* Correction Required

### Functionalities

* HR reviews onboarding submission
* HR can approve or reject
* System records approval timestamp

---

# 2.8 Activity Timeline

### Location

Employee onboarding profile.

### Logged Activities

* Employee created
* Documents uploaded
* Documents verified
* HR approval

### Functionalities

* Maintain audit trail
* Store timestamps for each event

---

# 2.9 Notification System

### Location

System-wide notification service.

### Trigger Events

